Description: Minimal development packages for JTSDK, WSJT-X, WSJT and WSPR
 These are the development components for the JTSDK Project.
 Included is everything you need to build or use JTSDK, WSJT, WSJT-X
 Excluding manpages and user guides. After installation, the meta package can
 be removed, however, doing so will affect future updates for development
 packages. For this reason, it is recommended that you keep the meta package
 installed.

