Description: Minimal plus user guide dev packages for JTSDK, WSJT-X, WSJT and WSPR
 These are the development components for the WSJT / JTSDK Project. Included is
 everything you need to build or use JTSDK, WSJT-X, WSJT and WSPR
 including user guide, but Excluding manpages. After installation, the meta
 package can be removed, however, doing so will affect future updates for
 development packages. For this reason, it is recommended that you keep the
 meta package installed.

