Description: Minimal plus manpage and user guide packages.
 These are the development components for the WSJT / JTSDK Project.
 Included is everything you need to build or use JTSDK, WSJT-X, WSJT and WSPR,
 including manpages and user guides. After installation, the meta package can
 be removed, however, doing so will affect future updates. For this reason,
 it is recommended that you keep the meta package installed.

